The Herald Tapiwa Bepe In this week’s section of profiling the Zimbabwe Stock Exchange (ZSE) stockbrokers, we feature Jemina Capital  (Private) Limited. Meet your Stockbroker Name:  Christopher Mugona Firm:  Jemina Capital (Pvt) Ltd Position:  Chief Strategist – Multi-Asset Experience: Mugona is a CFA charter holder and has over 23 years experience in the investment banking and stockbroking industry working in various capacities. He is a holder of B Com Hons in Finance and speaks with gusto about stockbroking services. Deal origination, structuring and execution are his main turf and he joined Jemina Capital from Platinum Securities. He has been involved in structuring and execution of sizable ticket transactions. Company Profile Jemina Capital is a privately owned securities brokerage organisation, whose aim is to have a long-term impact by providing extraordinary value for their clients while also creating generational wealth for their investors. Service Offering Jemina Capital offers the following services; Securities trading Custodial services Advisory Research Direct market access Target Market The clientele of Jemina Capital includes institutional investors, high net worth and retail individuals. The set minimum investment When investors go directly to Jemina Capital to invest on the ZSE, the set minimum is US$100 equivalent in local currency. Contact Details Cell: +263 772 883 604 / +263 719 883 604 Email: chris@jemina.capital Phone: +263-242-301752 Website: www.jemina.capital Facebook: JeminaCapital Twitter: @JeminaCapital LinkedIn: Jemina Capital Information provided in this article is for educational purposes only./For more information, visit www.zse.co.zw, email info@zse.co.zw, Tel: +263 24 2886830-5